<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.6.9">
<l>poyvaṇṇam maṉattakaṟṟip pulaṉaintuñ celavaittu</l>
<l>meyvaṇṇam niṉaintavarkku meynniṉṟa vittakaṉai</l>
<l>maivaṇṇam karumukilpōl tikaḻvaṇṇa maratakattiṉ</l>
<l>avvaṇṇa vaṇṇaṉaiyāṉ kaṇṭatuteṉ ṉaraṅkattē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My beholding of the sage in whom truth endures</l>
<l rend="indent">for those who meditate on truth’s form,</l>
<l>Having set aside the five senses, removing forms of falsehood from the mind,</l>
<l>The one whose color is the color of kohl, a color which glows like a dark cloud,</l>
<l>The color of an emerald, was in Araṅkam of the South</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
